  "design_notes": "The chart features a dynamic progression that mirrors the song's energy. S0 starts with sparse quarter taps, building into light 8th-note runs as the synths filter in. S1 acts as a highly dense transition with holds and rolls leading directly into the drop. S2 (The Drop) features intense streaming with light crossovers and syncopated holds to emphasize the strong accents. S3 cools down significantly with simple, sparse taps following the vocal phrasing to lead the player home safely.",
